value.0: This bed has a beaten straw mattress, lined with well worn cotton sheets and covered with a worn woolen blanket.  Tended quite well, washed and scented, you will not find any bedbugs living here.  Soft enough to allow even the most hard adventurer a decent nights rest.
Items placed in the storage chest will be saved permanently.  This is unique to each character, and the items can only be viewed/accessed by your player.
This sturdy blacksmith's anvil bears the dented sheen of long use. Something in you wonders what great weapons and armor have been shaped upon its well-worn surface.
A remarkable chest that seems to store gear persistently.
